  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b92\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "US cooperation will be fully available - US diplomats confirm meeting with PM",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "US diplomats visiting Sri Lanka have pledged US cooperation to make the negotiations with the International Monetary Fund a success and will extend the full support needed for public finance management.",
        "A diplomatic team comprising US Assistant Secretary of State for the Asian Region Robert Cabrot and US Assistant Secretary of State for South and Central Asian Affairs Kelly Gaitling arrived in the country on Sunday, the 26th.",
        "The group first met with the President and the Prime Minister today and held crucial discussions on what assistance could be provided to Sri Lanka in recovering from the current economic crisis.",
        "During its meeting with the Prime Minister on Monday, it pledged its full support for talks with the International Monetary Fund.",
        "US Ambassador to Sri Lanka Julie Sang also attended the meeting between the Prime Minister and US Diplomats.",
        "\"We met with US diplomats to meet with President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa to discuss Sri Lanka's economic crisis,\" he tweeted.",
        "At a time when Sri Lanka is facing serious challenges, we will continue to assist and extend long-term partnerships to help achieve a prosperous, secure and democratic future. ' said."
      ],
